I0gv7sOOUJw.title: Haig Papazian: Space Time Tuning Machine - Uncharted x Joe's Pub Live!
I0gv7sOOUJw.author: Joe's Pub
I0gv7sOOUJw.description:
Haig Papazian - the Lebanese-Armenian violinist, founding member of the influential band Mashrou’ Leila, architect and multi-disciplinary artist - will premiere selections from the first phase of his new solo work, Space Time Tuning Machine (STTM), a cross-disciplinary musical narrative exploring the multifaceted meanings of home.

Haig Papazian is a Lebanese-Armenian multidisciplinary artist, composer, and architect born in Beirut and currently based out of New York. He is a founding member and violinist of Mashrou’ Leila, the Lebanese band whose electro-pop anthems about political freedom, race, gender and modern Arabic identity have challenged the status quo of the Middle-Eastern music industry.

words, sounds, images, and machines by haig papazian
